### hardening windows ###
## links ##
https://tryhackme.com/room/microsoftwindowshardening



## exemples ##
Settings > Accounts > Sign-in Options							# manage signin option
Control Panel -> User Accounts and click on Change User Account Control Setting		# UAC enforce
Security settings > Account Policies > Password policy					# change password policy
Local Security Policy > Windows Settings > Account Policies > Account Lockout Policy 	# lockout policy
Control panel > System and Security Setting > System > Device Manager			# disable unused net device
Disable-WindowsOptionalFeature -Online -FeatureName SMB1Protocol			# disable SMB
C:\Windows\System32\Drivers\etc\hosts							# check hosts
arp -a											# check arp
arp -d											# clean arp
settings > Remote Desktop								# disable remote desktop
ms-windows-store									# microsoft safe store
Setting > Select Apps and Features							# config microsoft only
AppLocker										# config applocker
Settings > Windows Security > App and Browser Control > Reputation-based Protection	# active smartscreen
click “Privacy, Search and Services” - Set "Tracking prevention" to Strict 		# on EDGE
Click Start > Settings > Update & Security > Window Updates				# update windows ^^
Click Start > Search for 'Windows Features' and turn it on > Select Sandbox > Click OK	# win sandbox
msinfo32										# active secure boot
Settings > Update and Security > Backup							# enable filebackup





